"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Covered by:Ryan Gaydos,Paulina DedajandRyan Morik  Coverage for this event has ended.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.7513502810086959, \"rank\": 0.3309359919438177, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 532, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paulina_Rubio\", \"score\": 0.9673192776652806, \"rank\": 0.02044267441392805, \"text\": \"Paulina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paulina_Rubio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paulina_Rubio\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mijain Lopez\\u00a0is going out on top - which is where he has been for 16 years.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 596, \"end\": 608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mija\\u00edn_L\\u00f3pez\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mijain Lopez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mija\\u00edn_L\\u00f3pez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mija\\u00edn_L\\u00f3pez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Cuban won his first Olympic\\u00a0gold medal in 2008, and then five-peated on Tuesday with his victory in the Greco-Roman wrestling 130-kilogram division.\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\", \"score\": 0.8653739968969939, \"rank\": 0.11595540541893451, \"text\": \"Cuban\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the win, he became the first person to ever win an individual event five times at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 927, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lopez won gold in the 120-kilogram division in 2008, then did so again in 2012.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Four years later in Rio, the weight class than bumped up 10 kilos, and he won again.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1029, \"end\": 1032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999990867838355, \"rank\": 9.132170103834155e-07, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won another gold in the class in Tokyo three years ago, and did the\\u00a0same in Paris\\u00a0on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1131, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9998860991581702, \"rank\": 6.685456900446972e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999918435700683, \"rank\": 8.156496489181142e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After cementing his legacy, Lopez placed his shoes in the center of the mat, symbolizing his retirement.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What's great is the joy,\\\" Lopez said through a translator.\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a result that I was craving, but also for the whole world and my country.\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So happy to reach the Olympic elite.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The reward of a lifetime of working hard with the help of everyone and my family.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is my biggest win.\\\"\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is an excerpt from a report by Ryan Morik.\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1619, \"end\": 1623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9845287218084984, \"rank\": 0.015713916579529412, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the United States women's gymnastics team won gold in Paris,\\u00a0Simone Biles\\u00a0clapped back at a former teammate.\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1641, \"end\": 1654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9707233153231138, \"rank\": 0.01500742902616379, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1691, \"end\": 1696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999918435700683, \"rank\": 8.156496489181142e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1698, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tokyo Olympic gymnast MyKayla Skinner\\u00a0called out the 2024 team's work ethic, \\\"besides Simone,\\\" in a since-deleted video.\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1747, \"end\": 1752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9998860991581702, \"rank\": 6.685456900446972e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1769, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MyKayla_Skinner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MyKayla Skinner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MyKayla_Skinner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MyKayla_Skinner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles posted a collage of photos on Instagram showing her and her teammates carrying the American flag across the floor to celebrate their gold medal victory in the team final.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 2045, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.699506772028701e-14, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 1958, \"end\": 1971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999764676698017, \"rank\": 2.076515114029862e-05, \"text\": \"American flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In her post on Instagram, Biles did not mince words.\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2061, \"end\": 2070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 0.9999999954311534, \"rank\": 4.568805986364069e-09, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lack of talent, lazy, Olympic champions,\\\" she wrote.\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2153, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview with PEOPLE,\\u00a0Biles defended calling out her ex-teammate, saying she needed to take the \\\"team lead\\\" for her teammates as a three-time Olympian.\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2304, \"end\": 2312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999933705957222, \"rank\": 6.629388759758122e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's important because you have to teach them to use their voices.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And if not, you are a voice for the voiceless, which is okay,\\\" Biles said.\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just felt like it was right in that moment to stand up for them, because they are so young and they have not fully stood in their power yet.\\\"\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2602, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For somebody to stand up, I know it meant a lot for [my teammates],\\\" Biles added.\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is an excerpt from a report by Ryan Morik.\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2724, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995549795900783, \"rank\": 0.00044476875496468463, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Quincy Hall came from behind to win the men's 400m final for his very\\u00a0first Olympic gold medal.\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2737, \"end\": 2743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"score\": 0.9945275041578244, \"rank\": 0.004042444593884438, \"text\": \"Quincy\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the United States' first gold in the event since LaShawn Merritt in 2008 - it was the second year in a row\\u00a0the USA had swept the podium.\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2843, \"end\": 2856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.8007005548316901, \"rank\": 0.137678174151218, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2888, \"end\": 2903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LaShawn_Merritt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LaShawn Merritt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LaShawn_Merritt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LaShawn_Merritt\"}, {\"begin\": 2950, \"end\": 2953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9501541178246795, \"rank\": 0.05175188195319431, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the first medal for the United States since Merritt earned bronze in 2016.\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 3056, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3006, \"end\": 3019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7090371971712608, \"rank\": 0.15025969136669892, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3026, \"end\": 3033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LaShawn_Merritt\", \"score\": 0.999992100612126, \"rank\": 6.029604451944741e-06, \"text\": \"Merritt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LaShawn_Merritt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LaShawn_Merritt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hall finished the race in 43.40 seconds, a personal best - he was 0.37 seconds off world-record time.\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was in fourth place as he entered the straightaway, and by the looks of his face, he was going to give it 110%.\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hall did not take the lead until just mere meters away from the finish line, but it was enough to earn the title.\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3390, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Great Britain's Matthew Hudson-Smith\\u00a0finished just 0.04 seconds behind Hall to settle for silver, while Zambia's Muzala Samukonga won bronze with a time of 43.74.\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3408, \"end\": 3428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Hudson-Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 3496, \"end\": 3502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999143994707888, \"rank\": 4.9162953441437815e-05, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is an excerpt from a report by Ryan Morik.\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3592, \"end\": 3596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9956622005749178, \"rank\": 0.0024363281100209105, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Stars and Stripes looked like they were headed home without any hardware, but pulled off a miraculous comeback to eventually win in a shootout.\", \"from\": 3605, \"to\": 3752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Down 7-6 with just over 30 seconds to play, the United States was on a power play when Alex Bowen found the back of the net, eventually sending the game to a shootout.\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3802, \"end\": 3815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7090371971712608, \"rank\": 0.15025969136669892, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both the United States and Australia scored on their first two shootout attempts, but U.S. goalkeeper Adrian Weinberg blocked Australia's third shot.\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 4072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3932, \"end\": 3945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7090371971712608, \"rank\": 0.15025969136669892, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3950, \"end\": 3959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.5396435164126493, \"rank\": 0.8036688598104161, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4049, \"end\": 4058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.5396435164126493, \"rank\": 0.8036688598104161, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Bowen scored, the U.S. controlled their own destiny.\", \"from\": 4073, \"to\": 4130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4078, \"end\": 4083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Bowen\", \"score\": 0.9891170672782855, \"rank\": 0.01099314481768177, \"text\": \"Bowen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Bowen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Bowen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Round 4 saw both shot attempts blocked (Weinberg even made a save with his face), and after\\u00a0Australia tied the shootout\\u00a0in Round 5, a goal would have sent the United States to the semifinals.\", \"from\": 4132, \"to\": 4323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4224, \"end\": 4233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9878568317688453, \"rank\": 0.00861739730434293, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4291, \"end\": 4304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uni